Quickstrike:





Quickstrike flipped upside down under water. Got got most of the soot and 
black dust off as far as he could. He decided he may stay a little longer 
out here, not quite ready to return to the cave. In the Wild, he had plently 
of room and fresh air.

He surfaced, and at the shore he saw another bot, Lightmare. He screamed and 
splashed backwards. She caught him off-guard. His leg dropped, putting him 
underwater for a few seconds. He brough his head up.

"What in tarnation are ya doin'?" she shouted at her. "Ya scared th' slag 
outta me!"
